    dc:description "FIGURE 26–28. Aheatherella mira n. sp. (26) male, leg II, posterior view; (27) sternal region, arrow points to large pore-like structure, (28) opisthogaster, without marginal setae shown (including JV5, which sits slightly dorsally)." ;
